{"tid":1396572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要全民8月5罷工，首先要","createTime":"2019-08-02T06:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:54:02.000Z","uid":38404,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"784dde9158de17b09cae055ffdf32383f99a0b97","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>癱瘓全港交通</strong></span></span><br />\n身邊有好多人都驚罷工會冇咗份工，<br />\n但你諗下，而家出面被控嘅手足，<br />\n講緊最細只係十幾歲，<br />\n為嘅係我哋香港人嘅未來，<br />\n你唔敢請假罷工唔緊要，<br />\n我哋一於做環保撚，齊齊搭交通工具，幫你罷工！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵：每一條線嘅轉車站，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">荔景，青衣，美孚，太子，九龍塘，大圍，調景嶺，金鐘，香港，中環，尖東</span></span>，都係好好嘅戰線，之前都有車長講，要地鐵罷駛係冇可能，亂咁㩒停車制有可能犯咗附例，但我哋如果唔小心，跌咗嘢落路軌，人多閂唔到門，唔小心阻到列車正常運作，咁就唔算犯法啦<br />\n<br />\n巴士：地鐵搭唔到，自然會轉陸路。我識有啲車長其實想罷工，但冇辦法，始終有人唔敢。不過佢哋同我講，圍堵巴士廠冇乜用，因為好多車一早出咗廠，要大家罷工，一定係去隧道口轉車站，例如紅磡，大欖，咁先係最有效嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂，人多，就事成"},{"pid":"dbc12ce8eec69c7bd6f7f9df3c49fb065c4928c5","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03252ecddf9d7cbf6d63a620f114a67c53578ee9","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7c191504c45037f6616c7eb3bc988d315b1bf23","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"394b60b746b9ec5b29ac328116b033cc0af5ef88","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:47:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28be53e4a5671bc134b46213e2b4f6114fcc605d","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86265957e36a0d9863b6ee58581bafa2862dc88e","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d377f860d4bc3e11cb38d995d2a5ff24439af60","tid":1396572,"uid":38404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}